Our friendly IRC chatterbot for the #saunaklub hangout.

Current features include:

Command  | Function
---------|----------------------------------------
,aufguss | make random aufguss from aroma database
,joke    | al lowe's cyberjoke3000
,fortune | print fortune, accepts parameters
,meyers  | random effective series item
,rezept  | recipe of the day from chefkoch.de
,health  | files.saunaklub.net health information
,df      | print raid diskspace usage
